  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic driving physics</strong> — experience real traction, power balance, and weight distribution.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Advanced mechanical tuning</strong> — modify engine, suspension, drivetrain, and brakes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full visual customization</strong> — bodykits, rims, paint jobs, interiors, lights.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Testing and racing modes</strong> — fine-tune setups, push your limits, and improve lap times.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ongoing development</strong> — frequent updates, new parts, cars, and community-driven features.</p></li></ul>",
